Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:33.35,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Càng khí thế càng tốt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.39,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Hiểu rồi, khí thế chứ gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:40.93,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Tôi cần mua bánh mì gối!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.43,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Bánh gối?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.74,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Mang bánh mì gối ra đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.64,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Không tôi... bắn bỏ!
